Multi-talented creative musical genius, Big Star, has just released his second single over two consecutive weeks off his upcoming album Me&Mines titled Closer. Big Star’s Closer debuted yesterday as a 5FM exclusive playing on every show throughout the day, and will be supported by the following radio stations today just to name a few: YFM, Heart FM, Massiv Metro, UJ FM, TransAfrica Radio, Tshwane FM, EKFM, Bush Radio, Paragon FM and Yarona FM in Botswana just to name a few. Following the release of Big Star’s Time Of My Life single which he dropped last Friday, Closer is Big Star’s first radio single release to spearhead the journey to the release of his highly anticipated debut album. if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjsuDSrJElTV4LClaMn1vjJ6YERUg5N_sIhDaYVAr5L16fU-RQ8Exh_SrIbWDQf1xHyTKMblj-p9imF_buT0seG1RGc-ay_CF97R6aVELa8vemzpYS6Mz9XNCBsk-Vq_flPAyMBHO1nSasx1XD1qyTbF0YFhgtPKnY60JDMBiKTgnHsHQgOg9-B7JBtQ1gCuQnQIuIX8ZVKUgEWZp9af0d0ZieLfQ3HLBGeCZ--F1qgNEM14HemSKAkZ9T6CXwpFumE9NiMynRqPUMhv6aucWOIzVniiHXSQRRQvfGA\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzLqwzIkb928YEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
